(3650, 402, 'synopsis', 'This lesson covers the challenges, opportunities, and concerns involved in coming out or disclosing a hidden identity (e.g. Orientation, HIV Status, Level of Ability, etc.). The activities in this lesson will allow participants to think critically about how to establish networks and resources that can be used to assist in their coming out process.'),
