(4584, 454, 'synopsis', 'This lesson provides an introductory overview for client experience contributors (CECs) of intimate partner violence (IPV), it’s prevalence in the LGBTQ community, more specifically among Black men who have sex with men, and how to assess and support BMSM clients who may be experiencing IPV.'),
