(4664, 456, 'synopsis', 'This lesson provides an overview of the ways in which those who serve Black men who have sex with men (BMSM) can ensure they are treated with cultural humility and respect through intervening in moments when such practices are not observed by colleagues. This lesson will review what such instances look like and how to intervene when witnessing the mistreatment of BMSM.'),
