(4889, 462, 'synopsis', 'This lesson introduces participants to a discussion of relationship styles, dynamics, and values. Some of these relationship dynamics may be unfamiliar to participants, while others may be already engaged in them without being aware. Using both individual and large group activities, this lesson helps participants consider the  wide range of relationship styles and standards available to them.'),
