(4997, 465, 'synopsis', '<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">This lesson focuses on how to deal with the challenges of getting healthcare needs met due to barriers related to racism and homophobia within healthcare settings. This lesson will focus on harnessing self-efficacy and engaging supports. </span>'),
