(5744, 485, 'synopsis', 'This lesson provides psycho-emotional coping strategies for Black gay men who have experienced discrimination, violence, and internalized homophobia through their experiences with the Black church. This lesson utilizes interactive activities to help participants understand the skills that are available to them during periods of depression and/or anxiety.'),
