making of Black men in Baltimore, MD and Jackson, MS, in order to reduce HIV rates among Black men.\",\n        \"_paragraph\": \"field_5eaa7b20baafc\",\n        \"graph1\": 90,\n        \"_graph1\": \"field_5eaa7b2cbaafd\",\n        \"graph2\": 91,\n        \"_graph2\": \"field_5eaa7b51baafe\",\n        \"graph_caption\": \"may be diagnosed with HIV in their lifetime, if current rates persist.\",\n        \"_graph_caption\": \"field_5eaa7b5fbaaff\"\n    },\n    \"mode\": \"edit\"\n} /-->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Home', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '2-revision-v1', '', '', '2020-05-01 18:10:37', '2020-05-01 18:10:37', '', 2, 'http://swagtoolkit.test/2020/05/01/2-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
